metadata.title: Panacea 89635 Fan Pot Trellises, Green, 36" H, Pack of 3
description: Add classic support to your favorite potted plants with these Panacea Green Fan Pot Trellises. Placing a trellis within your planter encourages your flower or herb to grow upward, for robust and hardy flora. This set of 3 trellises each install into 5" diameter or larger planters, and their green finish meshes with your herbs or vines. The units expand outward toward the top, providing additional support as your plant grows, and the metal construction remains durable for several seasons. The triple pack creates a unified look in your sunroom or on your front porch, while the green tone of each enhances your plant. Help a few potted plants grow strongly with these Panacea Green Fan Pot Trellises.  This case pack contains 3 of the Panacea Fan Pot Trellises, Green, 36"H each.  Rail Dimensions: round rails, 0.125" dia. Dimensions: 4.5"W base, 15"W top x 36"H each Mounting: stake into soil Construction: metal
